#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "@react-canvas/core-v2 负责 Yoga 布局、CanvasKit/Skia 绘制与统一指针管线；@react-canvas/react-v2 把 React 组件接到这套画布运行时。"
#~ msgstr "@react-canvas/core-v2 handles Yoga layout, CanvasKit/Skia drawing, and a unified pointer pipeline; @react-canvas/react-v2 connects React components to this canvas runtime."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "@react-canvas/react-v2 只做组件层：把熟悉的 View / Text 接到同一套运行时 API，不负责替换 DOM。左侧导航与下文「能力示例」逐项对应，便于你对照行为与源码。"
#~ msgstr "@react-canvas/react-v2 is the component layer only: it wires familiar View / Text to the same runtime APIs and does not replace the DOM. The left nav and the capability cards below map one-to-one so you can compare behavior with source."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 命中与事件：hitTestAt、pointerEvents 与 dispatchPointerLike（捕获 / 冒泡）。"
#~ msgstr "• Hit-testing & events: hitTestAt, pointerEvents, and dispatchPointerLike (capture / bubble)."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 命中与事件：hitTestAt、pointerEvents（auto / none）、dispatchPointerLike 与合成 hover 的 enter / leave（方案 A，仅叶节点）。"
#~ msgstr "• Hit-testing & events: hitTestAt, pointerEvents (auto / none), dispatchPointerLike, and synthesized hover enter/leave (scheme A, leaf-only)."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 布局与快照：calculateAndSyncLayout、absoluteBoundsFor，布局提交后可订阅快照。"
#~ msgstr "• Layout & snapshots: calculateAndSyncLayout, absoluteBoundsFor; subscribe to snapshots after layout commits."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 布局与快照：calculateAndSyncLayout、absoluteBoundsFor；subscribeAfterLayout 读取提交后的 scrollY 等（见滚动示例）。"
#~ msgstr "• Layout & snapshots: calculateAndSyncLayout, absoluteBoundsFor; subscribeAfterLayout reads committed scrollY, etc. (see scroll demo)."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 绘制：CanvasKit 初始化与 Skia 呈现，支持位图 Image 与 SvgPath。"
#~ msgstr "• Drawing: CanvasKit initialization and Skia presentation; bitmap Image and SvgPath."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 绘制：initCanvasKit、attachSceneSkiaPresenter；舞台坐标与 DPR 通过 canvasBackingStoreSize 等与 backing store 对齐。"
#~ msgstr "• Drawing: initCanvasKit, attachSceneSkiaPresenter; stage coordinates and DPR align with the backing store via canvasBackingStoreSize."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 输入：attachCanvasStagePointer 合并 pointermove；clientXYToStageLocal 把指针映射到舞台本地坐标。"
#~ msgstr "• Input: attachCanvasStagePointer merges pointermove; clientXYToStageLocal maps pointer to stage-local coordinates."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "• 输入：attachCanvasStagePointer，指针坐标映射到舞台本地空间。"
#~ msgstr "• Input: attachCanvasStagePointer maps pointer coordinates to stage-local space."

