#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "attachCanvasStagePointer 把指针事件送进舞台，clientXYToStageLocal 换成舞台坐标；hitTestAt 按「同父级后插入在上」的规则取最深节点，pointer-events: none 会摘掉整棵子树。dispatchPointerLike 负责捕获与冒泡；hover 的 enter / leave 只在叶节点之间切换（README 所称方案 A）。"
#~ msgstr "attachCanvasStagePointer feeds pointer events into the stage; clientXYToStageLocal converts to stage coordinates; hitTestAt picks the deepest node using the rule that later-inserted siblings stack above under the same parent, and pointer-events: none prunes the whole subtree. dispatchPointerLike handles capture and bubble; hover enter/leave only swap between leaf nodes (README scheme A)."

