#: src/smoke/scenes/scroll-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "core-v2 未提供 onScroll；滚动时更新 scrollY 并 emitLayoutCommit。此处用 subscribeAfterLayout + getLayoutSnapshot()[scrollId].scrollY 驱动下方三角形（旋转 / 放大 / 缩小 / 淡出）。"
#~ msgstr "core-v2 has no onScroll; scrolling updates scrollY and emitLayoutCommit. Here subscribeAfterLayout + getLayoutSnapshot()[scrollId].scrollY drives the triangles below (rotate / grow / shrink / fade)."

#: src/smoke/scenes/scroll-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "core-v2 未提供 onScroll；滚动时更新 scrollY 并 emitLayoutCommit。此处用 subscribeAfterLayout + getLayoutSnapshot()[scrollId].scrollY 驱动下方多排三角形（旋转 / 放大 / 缩小 / 淡出）。"
#~ msgstr "core-v2 has no onScroll; scrolling updates scrollY and emitLayoutCommit. Here subscribeAfterLayout + getLayoutSnapshot()[scrollId].scrollY drives the triangle rows below (rotate / grow / shrink / fade)."

#: src/smoke/scenes/scroll-demo-scene.tsx
msgid "core-v2 未提供 onScroll；滚动时更新 scrollY 并 emitLayoutCommit。此处用 subscribeAfterLayout + getLayoutSnapshot()[scrollId].scrollY 驱动下方多排三角形（旋转 / 放大 / 缩小 / 淡出）。每排对 scrollY 做阶梯偏移（row × stagger），避免各排同相、看起来「后面不动」。"
msgstr "core-v2 has no onScroll; scrolling updates scrollY and emitLayoutCommit. Here subscribeAfterLayout + getLayoutSnapshot()[scrollId].scrollY drives the triangle rows below (rotate / grow / shrink / fade). Each row applies a stepped scrollY offset (row × stagger) so rows are not in phase and the lower rows don't look \"frozen.\""

