#~ msgid "initRuntime 同时持有 Yoga 与 CanvasKit；core-v2 的导出与框架无关。若在 React 里等就绪，可用 subscribeRuntimeInit、getRuntimeSnapshot 配合 useSyncExternalStore。"
#~ msgstr "initRuntime owns both Yoga and CanvasKit; core-v2 exports are framework-agnostic. In React, wait for readiness with subscribeRuntimeInit and getRuntimeSnapshot alongside useSyncExternalStore."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "initRuntime 拉起 CanvasKit，attachSceneSkiaPresenter 订阅布局提交后重绘。除 View 背景外，还支持 Image 与 SvgPath；canvas 与 DPR 的关系由 canvasBackingStoreSize 等与 backing store 对齐。"
#~ msgstr "initRuntime loads CanvasKit; attachSceneSkiaPresenter repaints after each layout commit. Besides View backgrounds, Image and SvgPath are supported; canvas vs DPR alignment goes through canvasBackingStoreSize and the backing store."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "initRuntime 聚合 Yoga 与 CanvasKit 单例，宿主可用 subscribeRuntimeInit、getRuntimeSnapshot 与 React 的 useSyncExternalStore 对齐就绪状态。core-v2 导出的 API 不绑定框架；react-v2 在 reconciler 里把 props / 函数式 style 落到 insertView、updateStyle、事件监听等调用上。"
#~ msgstr "initRuntime owns the Yoga and CanvasKit singletons; hosts can pair subscribeRuntimeInit and getRuntimeSnapshot with React's useSyncExternalStore for readiness. core-v2 APIs are framework-agnostic; react-v2 maps props and functional style in the reconciler to insertView, updateStyle, and event subscriptions."

