#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
msgid "这是一个运行在 Canvas 上的高性能 UI 渲染引擎，专为复杂的画布场景（如白板、设计工具、复杂数据可视化等）设计。底层的 core-v2 引擎提供了一套完整的 UI 运行时框架，而 @react-canvas/react-v2 让我们能用熟悉的 React 语法（View、Text 及 Hooks）来构建画布内容。"
msgstr "A high-performance canvas UI runtime for whiteboards, design tools, data viz, and more. core-v2 provides the full runtime; @react-canvas/react-v2 exposes View, Text, and hooks in React."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "这是跑在 canvas 上的 UI 运行时：布局用 Yoga，画面用 CanvasKit（Skia）绘制，指针与命中走 core-v2；@react-canvas/react-v2 把这些接到 React 的 View / Text 与 hooks，面向画布场景，不是拿来替代整站 DOM。"
#~ msgstr "A canvas-backed UI runtime: Yoga for layout, CanvasKit (Skia) for drawing, core-v2 for pointers and hit-testing; @react-canvas/react-v2 wires that to React View / Text and hooks. It targets canvas UIs, not replacing site-wide DOM."

#: src/smoke/scenes/intro-demo-scene.tsx
#~ msgid "这里用几句话说明本仓库在浏览器里实际跑什么：几何由 Yoga 算，帧由 CanvasKit / Skia 画，交互走 core-v2 的命中与派发；@react-canvas/react-v2 只把这一切包进组件与 hooks，不替代 DOM。"
#~ msgstr "In short, here's what runs in the browser: Yoga computes geometry, CanvasKit/Skia paints frames, and core-v2 handles hit-testing and dispatch; @react-canvas/react-v2 wraps that in components and hooks without replacing the DOM."

#: src/smoke/hooks/use-demo-catalog.tsx
